  "detailed_description": "Take a cruise through different countries. Relax as you enjoy the views, and tourists take pictures of their favourite landmarks. Take it easy - or not so much! But most importantly: <strong>be careful</strong>.<br><br><strong><u>Features:</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use your <strong>mouse</strong> to drive with the <strong>on-screen controls</strong>.<br></li><li>Game driven by <strong>physics</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>15 handmade levels</strong> set on <strong>3 different countries</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>Beautiful music</strong> unique to each country.<br></li><li><strong>Scoring system</strong> (don't crash, take the photo and beat the time mark).<br></li><li><strong>World leaderboards</strong> to see who is the fastest captain.<br></li><li><strong>Twitch integration:</strong> join the cruise of your favorite streamer and cross your fingers that you won't die if the captain has to crash.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/6e1b1112c0923f2438dd8298998f04ac.avif?t=1720815755\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br>You will be able to navigate through <strong>different countries</strong>, each with its own architectural style, environment and music. Close your eyes and feel like you are there, but not for too long or the consequences will be catastrophic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/e7a603fdbee9ae734f6214886f3d18e9.poster.avif?t=1720815755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/e7a603fdbee9ae734f6214886f3d18e9.webm?t=1720815755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/e7a603fdbee9ae734f6214886f3d18e9.mp4?t=1720815755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/14bdcfb0fae3833e8dbc201b3330fc1a.avif?t=1720815755\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br>Drive the cruise with a <strong>virtual rudder</strong>, which will make you feel like you're driving a real cruise ship. In addition, physics feel like real physics! So... remember to brake in time, waters are treacherous...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/a0a72963d7629097ddeda80222ad2beb.poster.avif?t=1720815755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/a0a72963d7629097ddeda80222ad2beb.webm?t=1720815755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/a0a72963d7629097ddeda80222ad2beb.mp4?t=1720815755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/93ac75b01577ed7182e16c92023807fe.avif?t=1720815755\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br>The important thing is to get there, no rush. Although... if you like <strong>challenges,</strong> you can <u>get rewards</u> if you manage to make the perfect journey in the shortest time possible.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/0b8ab75a31793cec4226831b64d5a1f6.poster.avif?t=1720815755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/0b8ab75a31793cec4226831b64d5a1f6.webm?t=1720815755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/0b8ab75a31793cec4226831b64d5a1f6.mp4?t=1720815755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/31f78ec20fea69fef13bf6d418e84ca3.avif?t=1720815755\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br>Take <strong>pictures</strong> of the landmarks unique to each level to go back home with a souvenir of your holiday.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/449b5508ed6a5099bc954b4f766d6409.poster.avif?t=1720815755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/449b5508ed6a5099bc954b4f766d6409.webm?t=1720815755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/449b5508ed6a5099bc954b4f766d6409.mp4?t=1720815755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/ffa6dc4b351a6134943c97cc9e48bdf4.avif?t=1720815755\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br>Currents, whirlpools and other <strong>obstacles</strong> will test your skills as a true cruise captain; let them sink in... but don't go too deep! You'll need them to avoid tricker sections!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/87a4f3a424409ae868d31ec5548e2e8e.poster.avif?t=1720815755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/87a4f3a424409ae868d31ec5548e2e8e.webm?t=1720815755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/87a4f3a424409ae868d31ec5548e2e8e.mp4?t=1720815755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
